| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1084 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 82cf3564-54ed-5fef-927d-c694a9c11f7d"
